ams, but he has the skills, the know-how, and a rational mind to balance it out.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":707},"end":{"line":8,"column":185,"offset":891}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":707},"end":{"line":8,"column":185,"offset":891}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"So first of all, learn to be optimistic and override your pessimism. Learn to dare, by doing and taking action. But be mindful and rational in the process and know that you will fail - many times over. As there's no other way to learn and gather experience. Be smart about it by keeping failures small and quick and retaining enough energy to keep iterating.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":895},"end":{"line":10,"column":359,"offset":1253}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":895},"end":{"line":10,"column":359,"offset":1253}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stay healthy and have enough energy. You have to work out and balance your emotions with rational decisions.","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":1257},"end":{"line":12,"column":109,"offset":1365}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":1257},"end":{"line":12,"column":109,"offset":1365}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"But stay out of the risk of ruin: jail, hurting yourself and gambling everything away. Instead take rational, optimistic bets with large upsides.","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1369},"end":{"line":14,"column":146,"offset":1514}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1369},"end":{"line":14,"column":146,"offset":1514}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reject most advice","p